    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Offer Letter</title>\n    <style>\n        /* Simplified Styles for Offer Letter */\n        .offer-letter-container {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            width: 210mm;\n            height: auto;\n            padding: 20mm;\n            background: #fff;\n            border: none;\n            margin:auto;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .header {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .header img {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: auto;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .header h1 {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            margin: 0;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .content {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .content p {\n            margin: 10px 0;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .content p strong {\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .content .section-title {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .content .section-content {\n            margin-left: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #777;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .footer p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n        .offer-letter-container .footer .contact-info {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"offer-letter-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <img src=\"{{company.logo}}\" alt=\"Company Logo\">\n            <h1>Offer Letter</h1>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <p><strong>Dear [Employee Name],</strong></p>\n            <p>We are excited to extend an offer for you to join <strong>{{company.name}}</strong> as a <strong>[Job Title]</strong>.</p>\n            <p>Your start date will be <strong>[Start Date]</strong>, and we are looking forward to welcoming you to our team.</p>\n            <p>Please find below the details of your offer:</p>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">1. Job Title and Department</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> [Job Title]</p>\n                <p><strong>Department:</strong> [Department]</p>\n                <p><strong>Location:</strong> [Office Location]</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">2. Salary and Benefits</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p>Your compensation package is as follows:</p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Base Salary:</strong> ₹[Base Salary] annually</li>\n                    <li><strong>Performance Bonus:</strong> ₹[Bonus Amount] annually</li>\n                    <li><strong>Health Insurance:</strong> Covered for you and your dependents</li>\n                    <li><strong>Retirement Plan:</strong> [Retirement Plan Details]</li>\n                    <li><strong>Paid Time Off:</strong> [Number of Days] per year</li>\n                    <li><strong>Stock Options:</strong> [Stock Option Details]</li>\n                    <li><strong>Other Benefits:</strong> [Additional Benefits]</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">3. Job Responsibilities</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p>Your primary responsibilities will include:</p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 1]</li>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 2]</li>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 3]</li>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 4]</li>\n                </ul>\n                <p>As an employee of {{company.name}}, you will be expected to uphold the values and policies of the company and contribute to the achievement of our goals.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">4. Terms and Conditions</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p>Your employment is contingent upon the following terms:</p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Probation Period:</strong> [Probation Period] months</li>\n                    <li><strong>Notice Period:</strong> [Notice Period] months</li>\n                    <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> You are expected to adhere to the confidentiality agreements as specified in the employee handbook.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Non-Compete:</strong> [Non-Compete Clause, if applicable]</li>\n                </ul>\n                <p>Additional terms and conditions will be outlined in the employment agreement and other official documents provided to you upon joining.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">5. Acceptance</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p>We kindly ask that you review the offer and confirm your acceptance by signing this letter and returning it by <strong>[Acceptance Date]</strong>.</p>\n                <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our HR department at <strong>{{company.hr_email}}</strong>.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <p>We are excited about the possibility of you joining our team at {{company.name}}. We are confident that you will make valuable contributions to our success.</p>\n            <p>Sincerely,</p>\n            <p><strong>{{company.name}}</strong><br>CIN: {{company.cin}}<br>Email: {{company.email}}</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <p>© {{company.year}} {{company.name}}. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p class=\"contact-info\">Contact us: {{company.hr_email}} | {{company.phone}}</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "title": "Offer Letter"
  }
  
