    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Experience Letter</title>\n    <style>\n        /* Styles for Experience Letter */\n        .experience-letter-container {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            width: 210mm;\n            height: auto;\n            padding: 20mm;\n            background: #fff;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            margin: auto;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .header {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .header img {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: auto;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .header h1 {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            margin: 0;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .content {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .content p {\n            margin: 10px 0;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .content p strong {\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .content .section-title {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .content .section-content {\n            margin-left: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #777;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .footer p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n        .experience-letter-container .footer .contact-info {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"experience-letter-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <img src=\"{{company.logo}}\" alt=\"Company Logo\">\n            <h1>Experience Letter</h1>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <p><strong>Dear [Employee Name],</strong></p>\n            <p>This is to certify that <strong>[Employee Name]</strong> was employed with <strong>{{company.name}}</strong> from <strong>[Start Date]</strong> to <strong>[End Date]</strong> as a <strong>[Job Title]</strong> in the <strong>[Department]</strong> department.</p>\n            <p>During this period, [Employee Name] demonstrated professionalism and dedication in carrying out responsibilities assigned to them. Some of the key tasks and achievements include:</p>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">1. Job Responsibilities</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <ul>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 1]</li>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 2]</li>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 3]</li>\n                    <li>[Responsibility 4]</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">2. Key Achievements</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <ul>\n                    <li>[Achievement 1]</li>\n                    <li>[Achievement 2]</li>\n                    <li>[Achievement 3]</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">3. Performance</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p>Throughout the tenure, [Employee Name] showed a great attitude towards their work, collaborated well with the team, and contributed to the overall success of the company.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <p>We are thankful for [Employee Name]’s contributions during their time with us and wish them all the best in their future endeavors.</p>\n            <p>Sincerely,</p>\n            <p><strong>{{company.name}}</strong><br>CIN: {{company.cin}}<br>Email: {{company.email}}</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <p>© {{company.year}} {{company.name}}. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p class=\"contact-info\">Contact us: {{company.hr_email}} | {{company.phone}}</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "title": "Experience Letter"
  }
