      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Promotion Letter</title>\n    <style>\n        /* Styles for Promotion Letter */\n        .promotion-letter-container {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            width: 210mm;\n            height: auto;\n            padding: 20mm;\n            background: #fff;\n            border: none;\n            margin: auto;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .header {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .header img {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: auto;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .header h1 {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            margin: 0;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .content {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .content p {\n            margin: 10px 0;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .content p strong {\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .content .section-title {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .content .section-content {\n            margin-left: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #777;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .footer p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n        .promotion-letter-container .footer .contact-info {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"promotion-letter-container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <img src=\"{{company.logo}}\" alt=\"Company Logo\">\n            <h1>Promotion Letter</h1>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <p><strong>Dear [Employee Name],</strong></p>\n            <p>We are pleased to inform you that, as a result of your excellent performance, dedication, and contributions to the company, we have decided to promote you to the position of <strong>[New Job Title]</strong> in the <strong>[Department]</strong> department, effective from <strong>[Effective Date]</strong>.</p>\n            <p>We believe that this promotion is a reflection of your hard work and commitment. Below are the details of your promotion:</p>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">1. New Position and Responsibilities</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p><strong>New Job Title:</strong> [New Job Title]</p>\n                <p><strong>Department:</strong> [Department]</p>\n                <p><strong>New Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>[New Responsibility 1]</li>\n                    <li>[New Responsibility 2]</li>\n                    <li>[New Responsibility 3]</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">2. Compensation and Benefits</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p>As part of this promotion, your compensation package has been updated as follows:</p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>New Base Salary:</strong> ₹[New Base Salary] annually</li>\n                    <li><strong>Performance Bonus:</strong> ₹[New Bonus Amount] annually</li>\n                    <li><strong>Additional Benefits:</strong> [Any New Benefits]</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"section-title\">3. Terms and Conditions</div>\n            <div class=\"section-content\">\n                <p>Along with the promotion, we would like to remind you of the following terms:</p>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Effective Date]</li>\n                    <li><strong>Probation (if any):</strong> [Probation Period]</li>\n                    <li><strong>Notice Period:</strong> [Notice Period] months</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <p>We trust that you will continue to excel in your new role, and we look forward to your continued success within our company. If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact the HR department at <strong>{{company.hr_email}}</strong>.</p>\n            <p>Sincerely,</p>\n            <p><strong>{{company.name}}</strong><br>CIN: {{company.cin}}<br>Email: {{company.email}}</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <p>© {{company.year}} {{company.name}}. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p class=\"contact-info\">Contact us: {{company.hr_email}} | {{company.phone}}</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "title": "Promotion Letter"
    }
    
